<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ شَيْءٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٢]</span> جائز، وهو مفعول <span class="c2">(حاملين)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>{لَكَاذِبُونَ <span class="c2">(١٢)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٢]</span> كاف.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
